posting_body: ['#$%#%Beautiful 2/2.5 bedroom is available at Quantum on the Bay desirable condo to be rented seasonally!SHORT TERM RENTAL 3 month’s minimum FULLY FURNISHED!!', 'This modern apt also features European style kitchen w/stainless steel appliances, New Samsung Washer /dryer, walk in closets, Enjoy amazing bay &city views!', 'At the Quantum offers a full suite of amenities including 2 heated pools, a 2 story gym, 24 hour security, theatre room, billiard room, sauna, party rooms etc.', 'Located across the Margaret Pace Park w/walking path, basketball, tennis & volleyball courts!', 'Walk to Publix, restaurants, shops and museums.', 'Come and enjoy Miami lifestyle Reside In 5 Star Luxury high rise with State of the art Amenities!', 'Close proximity to Downtown miami, Miami beach walking distance to Wynwood Art district !', '%$&', '#$%If you have been denied an application for lease in the past due to bad credit or your background, please call me or text me', 'show contact info', ', I will get you approved!!', 'Self-employed, bad credit, no problem.', 'Text me, I respond immediately and have tons of inventory!', 'WE ARE ESSENTIAL BUSINESS FOR COVI19, WE ARE ALWAYS OPEN', 'CALL ME OR TEXT ME', 'Andy Zamudio', 'show contact info', 'We accept deposits with credit card if you are short of cash we help with that, we are the only company that accepts credit cards for deposits , zelle, cash app, paypal venmo payments accepted!!!', 'Aceptamos los depositos con tarjeta de credito sinud esta corto de cash, somos la unica compañia que lo acepta en Florida, zelle, cash app, paypal ,venmo.']
